	<ns2959:title xmlns:ns2959="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP)</ns2959:title>
	<ns2960:para xmlns:ns2960="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
	OpenLDAP is an opensource implementation of the LDAP protocol, and can be used to create and maintain a shared address book, as well as provide centralised authentication to various operating systems and applications.
